28
00:02:56,447 --> 00:02:57,447
Mesej itu berbunyi...

29
00:03:01,247 --> 00:03:06,447
"Pertandingan Deduksi! Shinichi lwn. Subaru Okiya."

30
00:03:07,047 --> 00:03:09,546
Pesawat kertas jenis lain?

31
00:03:09,547 --> 00:03:12,146
