00:07:17,347 --> 00:07:19,147
Ini... Ini ialah...

118
00:07:21,347 --> 00:07:23,546
Tanda antena?

119
00:07:23,547 --> 00:07:25,247
Pada telefon bimbit?

120
00:07:28,347 --> 00:07:30,246
Yalah, ia kelihatan sama!

